      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with every system functioning exactly as intended and a comprehensive service history that confirms its meticulous upkeep. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and treated with the utmost care.",
